# Pinata IPFS Configuration
# Get your JWT token from https://app.pinata.cloud/developers/api-keys
# 
# Steps to get JWT token:
# 1. Go to https://app.pinata.cloud/developers/api-keys
# 2. Click "New Key" button
# 3. Give it a name (e.g., "DeCo Platform")
# 4. Enable "pinFileToIPFS" and "pinJSONToIPFS" permissions
# 5. Click "Create Key"
# 6. Copy the JWT token and paste it below

# Option 1: Use JWT (Recommended)
VITE_PINATA_JWT=your_pinata_jwt_here

# Option 2: Use API Keys (Alternative - not recommended)
# VITE_PINATA_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
# VITE_PINATA_SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key_here
